NOTE: Hive-CM8 and S4NDMAN are awesome for bringing us this to watch in english with direct line at such an early stage with a good video too so props to them and good job team :) i noticed the cam moved a few times so cut it into 4 parts and went to work on each piece, adjusting rotate, perspective, crop, the AR is on point all the way through and its straight more or less. :) also adjusted some gamma, gain, sat, hue, levels, contrast, it still has a couple of bright spots but nothing i could do to completely reduce them, its just how it was cammed,  then i muxed s4ndmans audio back to it and had to make 1 cut so it synced back in, enjoy.
